It's like the thing they have to
do to provide for their family.

00:35:43.310 --> 00:35:45.570
Like he says it's not
against the law of me

00:35:45.570 --> 00:35:47.730
as a husband and me as a father.

00:35:47.730 --> 00:35:49.710
