00:36:08.130 --> 00:36:11.520
As if their parents, who
sacrificed everything

00:36:11.520 --> 00:36:14.990
to cross the border, and
who work 18 hours a day,

00:36:14.990 --> 00:36:17.490
two or three different jobs so
their kids will have a better

00:36:17.490 --> 00:36:20.040
life-- as if they did
something wrong, right?

00:36:20.040 --> 00:36:22.009
So anyway, sorry.

00:36:22.009 --> 00:36:23.550
I'm just getting on
my soapbox there.

00:36:26.055 --> 00:36:28.505
It always really angers
me when people insinuate

00:36:28.505 --> 00:36:30.630
that their parents, who
have sacrificed everything,

00:36:30.630 --> 00:36:31.720
have done something wrong.

00:36:31.720 --> 00:36:32.220
OK.

00:36:35.700 --> 00:36:38.490
Anyway, so what I'm--

00:36:38.490 --> 00:36:41.051
sorry I just, like, really
