- And then there's just
this little second part

00:42:18.570 --> 00:42:24.360
where they are reacting after
they see a video from their--

00:42:24.360 --> 00:42:28.470
from her husband, and
they're reacting to it.

00:42:28.470 --> 00:42:29.820
He talks about how he wants to--

00:42:29.820 --> 00:42:30.486
[VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:42:30.486 --> 00:43:49.519
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

00:43:49.519 --> 00:43:51.435
[END PLAYBACK]

00:43:51.435 --> 00:43:58.620
[APPLAUSE]

00:43:58.620 --> 00:44:03.370
- So, it's very complex,
their situation.

00:44:03.370 --> 00:44:04.960
It's not that, like,
oh he's a jerk,

00:44:04.960 --> 00:44:06.310
you didn't send any money back.

00:44:06.310 --> 00:44:11.430
It's a very difficult thing
that a lot of these families

00:44:11.430 --> 00:44:13.420
go through.

00:44:13.420 --> 00:44:16.740
And even if he had been
sending money back,

00:44:16.740 --> 00:44:20.790
the women's roles are changing
because they're there alone

00:44:20.790 --> 00:44:22.770
with the kids, as well.

00:44:22.770 --> 00:44:28.300
So I definitely-- I wish
you could see the whole film

00:44:28.300 --> 00:44:30.580
because I don't want it to
seem like I'm demonizing

00:44:30.580 --> 00:44:33.420
her husband-- because he's
been through a lot as well,

00:44:33.420 --> 00:44:35.620
and he left with
all good intentions

00:44:35.620 --> 00:44:38.350
because he wasn't able
to survive financially

00:44:38.350 --> 00:44:39.850
there, and support
his family there.

00:44:39.850 --> 00:44:43.450
And he thought he could
do that in the US.

00:44:43.450 --> 00:44:44.570
I'm running out of time.

