migration from Mexico has
actually changed a lot

00:44:53.800 --> 00:44:55.720
since I made those two films.

00:44:55.720 --> 00:44:59.830
It's definitely gone down
since the recession of 2008,

00:44:59.830 --> 00:45:02.470
and even more so
in the last year,

00:45:02.470 --> 00:45:05.650
or so, because of the
current administration.

00:45:05.650 --> 00:45:08.500
Trump.

00:45:08.500 --> 00:45:10.300
So anyway, it's changed a lot.

00:45:10.300 --> 00:45:12.460
And a lot of--

00:45:12.460 --> 00:45:14.080
talking about gender
and citizenship,

00:45:14.080 --> 00:45:16.420
a lot of people
coming to the US now

00:45:16.420 --> 00:45:18.400
are women and children
from Central America.

00:45:18.400 --> 00:45:21.220
And the women are fleeing
domestic violence,

00:45:21.220 --> 00:45:25.210
or they're fleeing just
violence in their countries

00:45:25.210 --> 00:45:30.250
of Honduras, and
Guatemala, and I'm sorry--

00:45:30.250 --> 00:45:31.590
in El Salvador, right?

00:45:31.590 --> 00:45:36.880
Yeah, and so there's a lot
of-- and I sat with the asylum

00:45:36.880 --> 00:45:39.280
attorney and listened
to some women's stories

00:45:39.280 --> 00:45:40.270
a couple of months ago.

00:45:40.270 --> 00:45:43.630
And it's really awful
what's going on there.

00:45:43.630 --> 00:45:47.380
And so I know Trump is all
about sending National Guard

00:45:47.380 --> 00:45:48.490
troops to the border now.

00:45:48.490 --> 00:45:51.572
But I mean, these are women and
children fleeing gang violence.

00:45:51.572 --> 00:45:53.530
Where they're getting
murdered, their daughters

00:45:53.530 --> 00:45:55.930
are getting raped, and the
kids are forced to join gangs,

00:45:55.930 --> 00:45:58.410
and if they don't join gangs,
they'll also be killed.

00:45:58.410 --> 00:46:00.050
So I just wanted
to bring that up.

00:46:00.050 --> 00:46:02.440
And I have a new
film out that I've

00:46:02.440 --> 00:46:04.780
made with my colleague and
friend, Anayansi Prado,

00:46:04.780 --> 00:46:05.680
called The Unafraid.

00:46:05.680 --> 00:46:08.680
It premieres on Saturday,
but you can check it out

00:46:08.680 --> 00:46:10.100
on Facebook.

00:46:10.100 --> 00:46:11.200
You can see the trailer.

00:46:11.200 --> 00:46:14.170
It's called The Unafraid
documentary, if you search it,

00:46:14.170 --> 00:46:19.424
and it's about DACA
students and who belongs.

00:46:19.424 --> 00:46:29.798
[APPLAUSE]

00:46:29.798 --> 00:46:33.910
