00:46:53.054 --> 00:46:54.000
[APPLAUSE]

00:46:54.000 --> 00:46:54.500
- Hello.

00:46:58.360 --> 00:47:02.260
Latinos make up the largest
ethnic minority in the US,

00:47:02.260 --> 00:47:06.470
