00:47:21.120 --> 00:47:22.590
Loreta Velazquez.

00:47:22.590 --> 00:47:26.340
Because for over a century,
she's been dismissed as a hoax,

00:47:26.340 --> 00:47:29.040
even though contemporary
researchers have

00:47:29.040 --> 00:47:31.020
found her records in
the National Archives,

00:47:31.020 --> 00:47:35.490
in newspapers, and personal
papers of the time.

00:47:35.490 --> 00:47:39.900
And I'll share a short three
